com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast

Interface INumeric

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IFilterElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    INumericField, INumericInputArg, INumericLiteral, INumericScalarFunction

    public interface INumeric
extends IFilterElement
    Defines a common interface for all query elements that evaluate to enum types. INumeric instances can be acquired by using IQuery.newIntegerArg(), IQuery.newLongArg(), IQuery.newBigDecimalArg() or by traversing through a query model to a numeric field.
    Since:
    0.5
